pull_request.title: Allow forced no registration and POST method for setState
pull_request.body:
Allow the AP to explicitly store a state document with no registration by passing a registration of null in the configuration.

Allow the AP to specify it wants to use POST instead of PUT for application/json.

Supersedes https://github.com/RusticiSoftware/TinCanJS/pull/93

issue.title: I18n support for the module APIs
issue.body: Module APIs should be able to declare support for I18n and we should then use an interface to automatically install the correct l10n files for the installed modules based on the site's language.
